  "detailed_description": "<h1>Check This Out!!!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>A day after the original game's events, King Bearton is BACK with his new plan to take the Rhythm Knights out once and for all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/2d98857347c460aa8bacb73f0fd083a4.poster.avif?t=1665371936\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/2d98857347c460aa8bacb73f0fd083a4.webm?t=1665371936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/2d98857347c460aa8bacb73f0fd083a4.mp4?t=1665371936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The first game was not so hot... so this time, we brought the heat! The Rhythm Knights are back with all-new features! Rhythm Knights: Double Treble is a 2-4 key story-based rhythm game containing over 20 Levels! 7 of which are from Rhythm Knights: Reharmonized, the remastered release of the first classic which is included for free!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/879ab65d6d167ec3837cf060cb756d5d.avif?t=1665371936\" width=500 height=500 /></span><br><br>When the trouble is double, you know who to call.<br><br><strong>CREDITS:</strong><br>Dallen Larson - Director & Programmer<br>ZachJaDa - Artist<br>Noobstack - Music<br>Umbre - Guest Artist for Extra Pixels Level",
  "about_the_game": "A day after the original game's events, King Bearton is BACK with his new plan to take the Rhythm Knights out once and for all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/2d98857347c460aa8bacb73f0fd083a4.poster.avif?t=1665371936\" width=500 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/2d98857347c460aa8bacb73f0fd083a4.webm?t=1665371936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/2d98857347c460aa8bacb73f0fd083a4.mp4?t=1665371936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The first game was not so hot... so this time, we brought the heat! The Rhythm Knights are back with all-new features! Rhythm Knights: Double Treble is a 2-4 key story-based rhythm game containing over 20 Levels! 7 of which are from Rhythm Knights: Reharmonized, the remastered release of the first classic which is included for free!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1976180/extras/879ab65d6d167ec3837cf060cb756d5d.avif?t=1665371936\" width=500 height=500 /></span><br><br>When the trouble is double, you know who to call.<br><br><strong>CREDITS:</strong><br>Dallen Larson - Director & Programmer<br>ZachJaDa - Artist<br>Noobstack - Music<br>Umbre - Guest Artist for Extra Pixels Level",
